		"description": {
			"baseEffect": "<table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><p><strong>3 Actions, AoE</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"102,0\" colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>Concentration:</strong> Up to 1 minute.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><p><strong>Reach:</strong> 4.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><p>You become a cloud of tempestuous storm. You can fly, move for free 1/round, and attacks against you are made with disadvantage.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><ul><li><p>At the end of each of your turns, strike up to 4 creatures within Reach with a bolt of lightning for [[/r (1d8*10)+1d8]]{d88} damage (a creature can only be struck 1/round).</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><ul><li><p>+2 Reach and number of bolts each round. Costs 3 actions each round to maintain.</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" data-colwidth=\"102,0\"><p>Once you cast this spell, you must Safe Rest for 1 week before you can use it again.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
